  "detailed_description": "Cards of Patience combines solitaire-like gameplay with RPG and roguelite elements.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/48983964fa067ad791c1c37671d37289.poster.avif?t=1643140425\" width=480 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/48983964fa067ad791c1c37671d37289.webm?t=1643140425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/48983964fa067ad791c1c37671d37289.mp4?t=1643140425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Choose your hero and fight against a variety of enemies by destroying all their cards.<br>Use different levelable spells and equip yourself with powerful items and potions that will make your fights easier.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/327a3896ace8847a3603f337238da211.poster.avif?t=1643140425\" width=480 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/327a3896ace8847a3603f337238da211.webm?t=1643140425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/327a3896ace8847a3603f337238da211.mp4?t=1643140425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each run is different, but death is not the end:<br>Gain powerful diamond orbs through each victory that unlock permanent upgrades or even new heroes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/0c51ca2187a6bc663e6cb709ed1dd45c.poster.avif?t=1643140425\" width=480 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/0c51ca2187a6bc663e6cb709ed1dd45c.webm?t=1643140425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/0c51ca2187a6bc663e6cb709ed1dd45c.mp4?t=1643140425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br>- Turn-based card battles<br>- Different heroes with different talent trees<br>- A variety of items and potions<br>- Randomly generated<br>- Roguelite through permanent upgrades<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/4df46e2e0a3096bd266293a325763a47.poster.avif?t=1643140425\" width=480 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/4df46e2e0a3096bd266293a325763a47.webm?t=1643140425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/4df46e2e0a3096bd266293a325763a47.mp4?t=1643140425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
